rComments: Prof Rodriguez Hidalgo is such an incredible lecturer. She is so enthusiastic, and genuinely wishes for you to be interested in the material and do well. She is always helpful. I wish the class never ended, and this isn't something you always get to feel after a UofT course ends. The university needs more profs like her.
She tried her best to engage the whole class. Sometimes was difficult to understand her, but great prof nonetheless.
I think her accent was a bit of a barrier to learning (can't be helped), but she at least made sure that we (all 1500 of us) understood before moving on!
